Standard and Poor's Corp said it iskeeping Borg-Warner Corp's 400 mln dlrs of debt on creditwatchwith negative implications.    Under review are the company's A-plus senior debt and A-1commercial paper.    S and P cited an offer by a Merrill Lynch and Co-backedinvestment group's offer to acquire Borg-Warner for 3.76billion dlrs.    The purchase would increase Borg-Warner's financial riskand impair its earnings and cash flow protection, resulting ina debt leverage rise to a very high level, S and P said. Reuter&#3;